{{col-break}} * [[Abstract algebraic hierarchy]] *[[Borel hierarchy]] *[[Wadge hierarchy]] *[[Difference hierarchy]] * [[Tree (data structure)]] * [[Tree (graph theory)]] * [[Tree network]] * [[Tree (descriptive set theory)]] * [[Tree (set theory)]] {{col-end}}
